('Dr. Amina Hassan', 'Principal', 'Green Valley International School', 'Partnering with Thynkcity has revolutionized our computer science curriculum. Our students are now building real applications and competing in national coding competitions.', 5, 'approved'),
('Michael Chen', 'Business Owner', 'TechStart Nigeria', 'Thynkcity''s consulting services helped us build a robust e-commerce platform that increased our sales by 300%. Their expertise in African market needs is unmatched.', 5, 'approved'),
('Fatima Musa', 'Career Changer', '', 'I transitioned from accounting to data science through Thynkcity''s adult program. The flexible scheduling and personalized curriculum helped me land a role at a top fintech company.', 5, 'approved'),
('James Okonkwo', 'Student', 'Covenant University', 'The project management course at Thynkcity gave me practical skills I use daily. I''m now leading tech projects at my internship and feeling confident about my career path.', 5, 'approved');
